    Container of Connection instances that are all created with the same container parent and therefore share the same container Id.

    Client provided AdvancedMessage implementation that is used when sending messages from a ClientSender or when decoding an AMQP Transfer for which all frames have arrived.

    A dummy Tracker instance that always indicates remote settlement and acceptance for StreamSender instances.

    A dummy Tracker instance that always indicates remote settlement and acceptance.

    Tracking object used to manage the life-cycle of a send of message payload to the remote which can be stalled either for link or session credit limits.
    ClientRedirect
    Encapsulates the AMQP Redirect Map
    ClientSession
    Client implementation of the Session API.
    ClientStreamDelivery
    A StreamDelivery implementation that provides the mechanics of reading message types from an incoming split framed transfer.
    ClientStreamReceiver
    Client implementation of a StreamReceiver.
    ClientStreamReceiverMessage
    Streamed message delivery context used to request reads of possible split framed Transfer payload's that comprise a single large overall message.
    ClientStreamTracker
    StreamTracker implementation that relies on the ClientTracker to handle the basic OutgoingDelivery management.
    ClientTransactionContext
    Base for a Transaction Context used in ClientSession instances to mask from the senders and receivers the work of deciding transaction specific behaviors.
